listing.name: Authentic elite-class 1895  app totally renovated
listing.description:
Authentic dutch elite-class house from 1895 located in the high end zone of Amsterdam. Aristocratic old ceilings, ornaments mixed with new design kitchen, wooden floor and bathroom. Renovated since may 2015.

Close to old city, 5 minutes walk from musea and old historical buildings.
listing.house_rules:
No parties
No pets
No smoking
